0x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patricia-Clarkson-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patricia-Clarkson-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patricia-Clarkson-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2023 年间谍剧<em>《格雷》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>英国收视率排行榜上名列第二。</p><p>帕特里夏·<em>克拉克森 (</em> Patricia Clarkson) 饰演科妮莉亚·格雷 (Cornelia Gray)，她是一名中央情报局特工，因上级认为她是叛徒而躲藏了二十年。一名内奸开始泄露她原来单位的秘密后，她被带回来。</p><p>该剧还由鲁伯特·艾弗雷特、温迪·古逊、莉迪亚·韦斯特和肖恩·多伊尔主演。 《灰色<em>》</em>由狮门影业制作，于去年 9 月首次上映，但上映后在英国无法观看。 </p><figure id="attachment_3605963" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3605963" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3605963" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX.jpg" alt="Netflix 英国十大电视节目的屏幕截图。图片来源：Netflix" width="2000" height="1042" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX-400x208.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX-800x417.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX-696x363.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX-1392x725.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screengrab-of-Netflixs-Top-Ten-TV-programmes-in-the-UK.-Credit-NETFLIX-1068x556.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3605963" class="wp-caption-text"> Netflix 英国十大电视